{{地區用詞|cn=鳄梨酱|mo|tw=酪梨醬|hk=|start={{lang-es|Guacamole}}|as=稱為}}是[[美洲|美洲]][[阿兹特克|阿兹特克]]文化裡的传统调料，將[[鳄梨|鳄梨]]制成類似[[果酱|果酱]]的醬料，以便用来蘸着[[主食|主食]]（如[[墨西哥薄饼|墨西哥薄饼]]，{{lang-es|tortilla}}）吃。除了用鳄梨外，还可以加入[[洋葱|洋葱]]、[[辣椒|辣椒]]、[[大蒜|大蒜]]等等。“Guacamole”一词在[[墨西哥西班牙语|墨西哥西班牙语]]中发音近似“瓦卡莫雷”，而在[[美式英语|美式英语]]中发音近似“瓜克莫利”。「莫萊」或「莫利」（''mole''）在[[阿茲特克人|阿茲特克人]]說的[[納瓦特爾語|納瓦特爾語]]的意思，就是「醬料」，這個字亦隨着他們的文化而進入了墨西哥的西班牙語中。

在[[美国|美国]]，鳄梨酱很受欢迎，是年轻人开[[派对|派对]]时经常准备的零食，用来和炸[[馬鈴薯片|馬鈴薯片]]、炸[[玉米片|玉米片]]等一起食用。

== 词源与发音 ==
[[File:Guacomole.jpg|thumb]]
鳄梨酱的西班牙语词是“{{lang|es|Guacamole}}”，其源自[[古典纳瓦特尔语|古典纳瓦特尔语]]“{{lang|nah|āhuacamōlli}}”{{IPA-nah|aːwakaˈmoːlːi|}}，由词根“āhuacatl”<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.thoughtco.com/is-the-g-in-guacamole-silent-3079533 |title=How to Pronounce "Guacamole" in Spanish|work=ThoughtCo |trans-title=Guacamole 在西班牙语里如何发音 |language=en |access-date=August 20, 2018}}</ref> {{IPA-nah|aːˈwakat͡ɬ|}}（鳄梨）+ “mōlli”{{IPA-nah|ˈmoːlːi|}}（酱）。<ref name="zeldes">{{cite web |last=Zeldes |first=Leah A. |title=Eat this! Guacamole, a singing sauce, on its day |website=Dining Chicago |publisher=Chicago's Restaurant & Entertainment Guide, Inc. |date=November 4, 2009 |url=http://blog.diningchicago.com/2009/11/04/eat-this-guacamole-a-singing-sauce-on-its-day/ |access-date=November 5, 2009|url-status=dead|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100323081500/http://blog.diningchicago.com/2009/11/04/eat-this-guacamole-a-singing-sauce-on-its-day/|archive-date=23 March 2010}}</ref>

“Guacamole”，在[[墨西哥西班牙语|墨西哥西班牙语]]中发音是 {{IPA-es|wakaˈmole|}}（近似于“瓦卡莫雷”）；<ref>{{cite book|editor=Claudia R. Guerra|title=300 Years of San Antonio and Bexar County|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=6ilbDwAAQBAJ&pg=PT55|year=2018|publisher=Trinity University Press|location=San Antonio, TX|isbn=9781595348500|page=55}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|author1=Maria de Lourdes Santiago Martínez|author2=Juan López Chávez|title=Etimologías: introducción a la historia del léxico español|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=lKuajvrBhzsC&pg=PA241|year=2004|publisher=Pearson Educación|isbn=9789702604938|page=241}}</ref> 在[[美国英语|美国英语]]中倾向于发音为 {{IPAc-en|ˌ|ɡ|w|ɑː|k|ə|ˈ|m|oʊ|l|iː}}（近似于“瓜克莫利”）；在[[英国英语|英国英语]]中发音为 {{IPAc-en|ˌ|g|w|ɑː|k|ə|ˈ|m|əʊ|l|eɪ}}（近似于“瓜克莫雷”）。<ref>{{cite web |title=Definition of guacamole in English by Oxford Dictionaries |url=http://www.oxforddictionaries.com/definition/english/guacamole |website=Oxford Dictionaries English |access-date=21 August 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://lifebyyou.com/us/detroit/food/guac/rock-your-guac-2018.html|title=Etymology|access-date=August 12, 2018}}</ref>

